Author: grossenten98
Text: Just eat what you want, I only recovered when I quit seeing my RD and Therapist. It’s easier to be normal when you’re not getting labeled ‘abnormal’. Besides, my dietician triggered me so MUCH! She was like competition ngl

Author: grossenten98
Text: Carbs aren’t the only brain power. ( r/ketoscience )  But, this morning I ate 2 T-Bone steaks for breakfast because I’m so fed up with people telling me that “carbs are brain power”. And because I’m a freaky rebel XD
